Michael Culver https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Culver 0 Michael Culver (born 16 June 1938) is an English actor. He was born in Hampstead, London, the son of actor Roland Culver and casting director Daphne Rye. He was educated at Gresham's School. Michael_Culver ( born_16_June_1938 ) is an_English_actor .
